sources.title: Crash of Moons (1954)
sources.description: A three-part episode from the TV series Rocky Jones, Space Ranger edited together and released as a feature for 16mm rental only. Season 1 episodes 21, 22, 23.  Episode 21: Rocky saves a space station and his friends when they are trapped between gypsy moons. Episode 22: Cleolanthe tries to destroy one of the gypsy moons with a barrage of missiles. Episode 23: Rocky evacuates the gypsy moon Posetta and stops Cleolanthe's missile barrage. Watch on RetroFlix:  https://retroflix.org/crash-of-moons-1954/

sources.title: Crash of Moons (1954) ROCKY JONES, SPACE RANGER
sources.description:
Stars: Richard Crane, Scotty Beckett, Sally Mansfield
Director: Hollingsworth Morse

You've heard of The Lone Ranger, now meet The Space Ranger! Follow the adventures of Rocky Jones and crew as they cruise the galaxy in their Orbit Jet X-V2 and defend Earth against space-bound evil doers!

sources.title: Crash of Moons (1954) Adventure, Sci-Fi, TV Movie
sources.description:
Rocky Jones and crew take action when an impending celestial collision threatens two civilizations. 

Director: Hollingsworth Morse
Writer: Warren Wilson
Stars: Richard Crane, Scotty Beckett, Sally Mansfield
Genres: Adventure | Family | Sci-Fi

metadata.Plot: This was never released as a feature film but, instead, is comprised of 3 episodes from the TV series, Rocky Jones, Space Ranger (1954) which were edited together and released on video as a feature-length story.
metadata.Actors: Richard Crane, Scotty Beckett, Sally Mansfield
